<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1208:1231'>疏衰裳齊者疏猶麤也齊者緝也此衰齊三年章以輕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1231:1254'>於斬故次斬後上斬衰章中為君三升半曰麤衰以三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1254:1278'>升正服斬不得麤名三升半成布三升微細則得麤稱晏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1278:1301'>子麤衰為在三升斬内以斬為正故設義服之此疏衰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1301:1324'>四升始見其麤若然為父哀極直見深痛之斬不没人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1324:1347'>功之麤至於義服斬衰齊衰之等乃見麤稱其大功小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1347:1370'>功更見人功之顯緦麻極輕又表細密之事皆為哀有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1370:1394'>深淺故作文不同者也則斬衰先言斬者一則見先斬其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1394:1420'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '016-5a' );" name="016-5a" class="pb">[016-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1420:1443'>布乃作衰裳二則見為父極哀先表斬之深重此齊衰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1443:1466'>稍輕直見造衣之法衰裳旣就乃始緝之是以斬衰斬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1466:1475'>在上疏衰齊在下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1475:1501'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '016-6a' );" name="016-6a" class="pb">[016-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
